Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.27,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:14.28,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey! My name is Goda Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.51,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:22.68,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonight's master is the world-famous ballerina, Miss Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.49,Petto_basic,woman,0,0,0,,Takeshi-kun, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:26.72,Petto_basic,woman,0,0,0,,Please come in…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:31.73,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:35.23,Petto_basic,woman,0,0,0,,… is what I want to say, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:38.87,Petto_basic,woman,0,0,0,,Sorry, my boyfriend is here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:40.10,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.14,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,You're kidding me, Hashimoto Shinya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.48,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Wa-wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:58.52,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ouch, that hurt…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.59,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It hurts more than Sumire-chan's flick on the forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:19.01,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this moment, I am a wandering alley dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:22.48,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Is this sensei? It's me, Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:25.61,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,I lost track of Takeshi-san's whereabouts again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:28.18,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:30.62,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Relating the circumstances up until now…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:34.49,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,This is only my guess, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:41.56,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san, who has been sleeping in a hotel around Minatoku City since mid-March
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:50.11,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,was asked by the hotel owner to pay back the hotel fees with his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.99,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,And she demanded that he have a physical relationship with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.99,0:01:54.41,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Stop it, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:58.68,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, man… please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:07.02,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,I'll get you, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.56,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Hey, punk! You disrespect the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.56,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,The men who went after him beat him to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.77,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,He was barely hanging on for dear life, and went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:24.14,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,There's no way we can find him! The owner's going to yell at us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:37.05,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,And in some ways, he was saved by a young female journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.29,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.59,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,And went to live at that woman's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:47.00,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,He was very happy and his life there lasted for almost two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.40,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,But for some reason, they had a conflict of interests and…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Never come back, you stupid pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.31,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,He's been nowhere to be seen since last weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.61,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,The pet fought with you and ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.89,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,What exactly happened? In detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:12.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,In detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.99,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Did he try to force himself on you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.93,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, no… it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:21.76,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Then how did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just that, even though he's a pet, he was being really saucy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Well, I was also at fault for causing the whole thing to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.60,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Who seriously fights with their pet like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I didn't know he was so strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He never disobeyed me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:37.71,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if you could let me stay over tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.12,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I knew it. You came here because you felt lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.35,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,That's it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.72,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You can't stand the loneliness of being in that house all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:49.96,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's not how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.09,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just that being by myself, I feel like I'm being crushed by the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.90,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,People call that "loneliness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.47,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Geez, you're so hard to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I know, I won't try to deny it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.74,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why don't you go to your boyfriend's and seek some comfort there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I don't want to be a bother to senpai when he's so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:09.61,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,And that means you can be a bother to a housewife like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no no no… That's not what I meant at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I apologize. I'll go home as soon as I drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:22.36,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hey, can I say something that's been on my mind for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:22.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.70,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'll put it bluntly. Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:28.86,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.07,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're stupid. There's something wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.77,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,If you had any common sense, there's no way this would be allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.94,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Outside, you're going out with an awesome boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.24,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,But at home, you're being healed by a cute young man who is your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:42.31,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Something that wonderful won't ever continue for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:45.08,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're a career woman or a Tokyo University graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.62,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,The one who's being conceited is not your pet, but you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:52.15,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,And having all that, you're still lonely and I should let you stay at my house? You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm plagued by household duties and chores and pass every day without anything that heals or rewards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.03,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about how that might feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.93,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Never, right? Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:03.43,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You should just reflect on your spoiled life up until now, and feel lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:09.20,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh~! Now that's off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.87,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not like I didn't know that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.64,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,What is it? You can talk back if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:18.88,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Hasumi-san too… having a secret like that held from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.92,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,And for that pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.06,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're going home? I thought you were gonna stay for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's not like I'm lonely or anything, and what you say is always correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.99,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.63,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,My brother left it before he went on vacation, so can you take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:42.50,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,This is a normal pet. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.68,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Anyway, you were going to end it someday, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:58.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Well, I knew I couldn't let it carry on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.03,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:10.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He didn't have to leave like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.23,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.89,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hello, Iwaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.17,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.07,title,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Kimi wa petto\NYou are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.07,episode,text,0,0,0,,7. Let's go home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.84,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.67,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.27,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Can you just let me stay over tonight? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.91,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, and can I have that adult video I lent you the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:26.78,Petto_basic_2,Junpei,0,0,0,,I haven't borrowed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.00,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Why are you coming to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.98,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Because all the ladies turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.78,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I don't care! You and I just fought, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.68,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.35,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I don't like you anymore! Go home to your lady friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.59,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I don't like myself either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.63,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But I did like Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.16,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Momo? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:53.90,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Momo was a really good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.54,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I won't let you stay over, but hang around for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.25,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.08,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Earlier… I thought you were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no… I wasn't crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:15.22,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,At that moment, they were showing a documentary on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And I felt kind of moved…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.83,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.76,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I panicked and came over right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:27.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Have you eaten dinner yet? Shall I fix you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.44,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,All right, I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:40.25,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Momo-chan. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:48.92,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Your birthday is the day after tomorrow, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.33,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.36,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.87,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes. Things have been pretty hectic lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.53,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see. You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:02.90,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Do you want to go out and get something good to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:05.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:15.62,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Only a little over one week before the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.49,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:27.13,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hey, do you remember what day the 31st was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:31.90,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I don't know. Isn't it just the end of the month?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.04,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,That's true…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:39.21,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Oh, did you know that the brave youth Perseus can fly in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.38,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What? Is that my role?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.00,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,He wears winged shoes and rides the flying Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:49.15,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,And he saves the princess who is tied naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.59,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,A flying hero…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.66,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Sounds cool. It kind of fits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:56.96,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.83,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Always flying around freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.63,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,It's something I could never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:34.50,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Even when we're together, I feel uneasy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:40.84,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,She was always kind of awkward in her manner, and has loved her life in an uptight way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:46.17,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Even while sleeping, she furrows her brow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.21,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Was it a little scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.75,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes, a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.98,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,She looked like she was in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.12,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Maybe she was having a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.92,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I hope that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.99,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Was it the first time you spent the night together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:06.29,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes, although we didn't have intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.40,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I don't feel the need to rush that though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.87,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'd rather feel stability.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.74,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Do you want to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:15.90,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes, I am thinking of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:21.48,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm always moving around, so I want to have a place where I can settle down. That's what I've always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.44,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.08,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,In that aspect, she is very ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.65,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Is she family-oriented?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.70,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:31.69,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This morning she apologized several times, saying "I'm sorry for falling asleep",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.06,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,and prepared a delicious breakfast for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:40.03,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,She is very gentle, beautiful and excels in her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.23,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,And she's flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:41.90,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:42.83,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:47.04,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean… I am very envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:53.98,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But I know for sure that she does not feel at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:59.51,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I wish she'd at least open up and be herself in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.88,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But it seems difficult…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:04.09,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It seems like I'm losing to even a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.06,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You are also feeling pressured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.13,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That may be so, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.73,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.53,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You have a very nice smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.20,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You are a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:24.14,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Doctor, may I see you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.38,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello, nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.82,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to see you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.03,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I have an appointment after this, and I couldn't reschedule it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But my headaches and insomnia are as bad as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.57,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.47,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,my pet has disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.84,Petto_basic_2,counsel,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.67,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,"My pet this, my pet that" is all you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:02.34,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You're an idiot of a woman who can't even understand a man's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.30,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.95,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,To let such a woman in while I'm in the middle of a counselling session!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.35,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.89,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,The worst… you two are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.83,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.43,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Shall we stand for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.40,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.54,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Relax, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.61,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh… relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.71,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes, let's live life carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:42.62,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,We men always carry an unconscious pressure which women never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.72,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It's the result of the systematization which makes us the head of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.29,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It's a given that we're strong. It's a given that we are the breadwinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:52.40,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,A given that women protect the family, etc., etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.60,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,And women rarely notice that type of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:56.23,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:14:02.90,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,But women these days are strong-headed. It's become a difficult world for men to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.17,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You may have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:08.38,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What's wrong with liking young women with big breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:13.25,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Women also like those ripped young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.20,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.80,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:21.26,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Their desire to corrupt young men makes women today seem stronger than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.02,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:25.50,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Then women should also take responsibility and be reprimanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:27.90,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,There is no reason for men to shoulder the heavy burden by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:32.63,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But I want to become a support for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.34,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.07,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You can't spoil her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:44.98,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,For you to want her to be at peace, means giving her even more pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:48.18,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see… I think that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.59,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,There's absolutely nothing wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:53.36,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Now, let out all the tension in your body, and let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is it with everyone calling me stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.77,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're Goda Takeshi's dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.88,Petto_basic_2,Rumi,0,0,0,,I'm Takeshi's ex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.63,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I don't want anything, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:36.93,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:41.94,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,It's really low of you to make a young man a pet when you work at such a big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.71,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Takeshi's not the kind of guy that should be made a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:50.61,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,He's an elite ballet dancer and has won a lot of awards since he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:53.78,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Even in modern dance, he's what we all aspire to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.85,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,If you're going to pay someone to comfort you, then go find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not like that. Momo is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.89,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Who the hell is Momo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:07.70,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,You're doing the same thing as those old men who surround themselves with young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.50,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Elite women are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.54,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I never want to grow up to be an adult like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.27,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I won't let you have Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:26.01,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Hmm… now I see how things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:36.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of course… yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.30,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,She's… acting a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:46.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I understand. I understand now. It's exactly how everyone says things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.24,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:52.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,On top of that, I just lost to him, and he made me make him a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:58.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I didn't even plan on keeping him that long. I don't know why I'm feeling all emotional now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:03.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was just taking care of an abandoned dog for two months, and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,So from tomorrow onwards, I think I'm going to look forward and just enjoy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:08.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Enjoy my present petless life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.06,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.83,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,It's good to look towards the future and all, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm looking towards the future, I'm happy, and I feel very refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.86,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Now I won't have any secrets to keep from senpai either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go over there to return your dog later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must have hurt him a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:44.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time… and that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:46.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He won't come back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.31,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo is no longer in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.42,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.37,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ruff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.63,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll become your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:32.74,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just needed a place to stay. A temporary place to stay until I go to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.11,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.88,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Anywhere was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.79,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why am I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.77,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I can't become some kind of a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.95,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That tickles, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.36,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What the… it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.40,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.13,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.80,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.27,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:44.08,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,You haven't sent your application to Germany yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:47.18,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,She said that if you're struggling with a lack of money, she wants you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.82,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Mom did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:50.90,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:55.29,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Even in contemporary dance, Frankfurt Dance Theatre is very famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:20:01.00,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,If you still have the will to continue dancing, sensei said she wants to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:01.86,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.73,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I can get the money from welfare anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.50,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Then is there a reason why you're hesitating to go on the foreign exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.31,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,No, nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:23.28,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Did Dad and Mom divorce yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:24.89,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.72,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So you're still helplessly in love with Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.76,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,What are you saying? I'm just a business-related…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.60,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.24,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Pas de chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.98,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It was the first ballet move you taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.21,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.25,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,It was when you were three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:07.33,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Back then, it was just fun to dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:13.64,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But Mom and Dad were always fighting because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:19.11,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So if the foreign exchange and competition worked out for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:24.45,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I thought that maybe they would get along better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:43.26,Petto_basic,mother,0,0,0,,Takeshi, you are my pride and joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.27,Petto_basic,mother,0,0,0,,Whatever your father may say, I'm going to make you continue ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:56.04,Petto_basic,mother,0,0,0,,Takeshi, make your mother's dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:04.65,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,The joy of meeting the expectations of the person you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:08.82,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But the expectation kept growing, and it became a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:12.19,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,The joy transformed into the fear of letting that person down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:19.03,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I just didn't understand after a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:21.54,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,the reason I was dancing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:28.48,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,But Takeshi-san, you were always my bird of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:39.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What a good boy, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:43.43,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I just wanted a hand that would accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:44.89,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:49.83,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm not sure either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:55.37,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Please go see your mother before going to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:57.41,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,You haven't seen her in four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:08.78,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a performance soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:12.32,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's contemporary dance, which Mom hates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:17.03,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Tell her to come see if she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:27.04,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,As I explained earlier, the situation is like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.04,0:23:29.00,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,What is that? A complaint call?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:32.21,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,It's from the same guy. He's so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:34.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,About that, like I've been saying…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:37.85,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He hung up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:39.85,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:42.92,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,If he calls again, let me answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:45.52,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,With people like that, it's better if a man yells at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.02,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Yeah, you should just leave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. It's concerning my own article, so I'll deal with it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:54.26,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,You're really not cute. That's why it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.13,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean, it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:23:58.77,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:01.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Can you explain to me in detail, why it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:05.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can understand if I was avoiding the blame, but I'm trying to take the responsibility here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:06.81,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't understand why I have to be talked to like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:09.94,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,It's not like we need you to take on all the responsibilities by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:11.61,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,We can do just fine without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.70,0:24:30.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Is that you, Fukushima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.50,0:24:32.70,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Oh! It's you, Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.77,0:24:37.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Did you forget to wash your face before you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.44,0:24:39.00,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,What kind of a joke is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.00,0:24:41.38,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I just came to fix my makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.11,0:24:44.48,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,In the afternoon, my foundation starts coming off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:48.15,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Would you like to try it too, Iwaya-san? Maybe you'll look a little prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.85,0:24:52.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm too busy and don't have such time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:55.46,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I guess elite people don't have to worry about trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.96,0:24:59.79,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Although it must feel good to work hard and raise your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:04.27,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,So what? There are many people who can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.47,0:25:13.78,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm me. I just do things the way I see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.42,0:25:23.12,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I know you're actually not that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.47,0:25:40.50,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,That woman frustrates me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.50,0:25:41.37,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Calm down, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.37,0:25:45.07,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Due to hormonal imbalance, women's ups and downs are apparently more extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.07,0:25:47.14,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,That's why I don't want to work with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:51.18,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Well, you'll never know how long she'll be working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.18,0:25:53.15,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.15,0:25:56.05,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,I heard that Hasumi-kun may return to Rio de Janeiro again in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:57.39,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.52,0:25:59.95,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Rio de Janeiro's Yoshimoto-san collapsed, right? So he may have to go in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.95,0:26:02.66,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,I wonder what that woman is going to do then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.86,0:26:04.43,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.30,0:26:19.99,note,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Nioi-sumire (violets)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.58,0:26:24.38,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hey, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.02,0:26:29.18,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You're Iwaya-san's…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.86,0:26:38.53,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan's ex-boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.10,0:26:47.47,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.17,0:26:50.81,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,This is the pet advice room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.37,0:26:53.84,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What happened to Momo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.84,0:26:56.51,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, that doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.81,0:26:58.05,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.68,0:27:03.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's fine. The pet got sick of me and ran away. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.85,0:27:04.85,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Got sick of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.99,0:27:07.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.42,0:27:10.23,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a case where the pet got sick of its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.23,0:27:11.66,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It's not like a man-woman relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.03,0:27:12.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.33,0:27:14.40,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.40,0:27:17.43,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Between a pet and a master, there's a relationship of superiority and inferiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.43,0:27:19.93,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,That's why the pet will never betray its master,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.93,0:27:24.01,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,and it's also why the master feels the responsibility to care for the pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.01,0:27:26.94,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,The pet also needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.74,0:27:32.08,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,The only person in the world that can protect the pet is its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.58,0:27:34.65,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,There is no one to replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.60,0:27:54.67,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Oh, doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:27:57.91,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about what happened with Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.91,0:28:01.44,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,No, I was the one who was being rude… it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.81,0:28:08.25,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I can only be grateful for your return, despite all the awful things I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.25,0:28:12.49,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.69,0:28:17.86,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,This weekend, would you like to walk our dogs together?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.33,0:28:19.03,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.03,0:28:23.03,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I came back here because my wife's giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.73,0:28:24.90,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.90,0:28:27.04,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So you're going to be a father soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.04,0:28:30.94,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, your flowers were blooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.67,0:28:32.91,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Nioi-sumire?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.24,0:28:36.54,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.88,0:28:42.38,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I gave it to her right around this time last year… for her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.26,0:28:51.39,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Umm… there's something that's been on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.86,0:28:57.77,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You're one of those… guys that live off a woman's money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.47,0:29:01.27,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,No, I'm a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.40,0:29:06.57,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's worse because it means I'm pretty much useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.44,0:29:11.11,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I want her to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:18.12,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I don't want you to do anything that would hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.79,0:29:24.13,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, I probably wouldn't hurt her as much as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:27.96,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,That's true, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.80,0:29:36.71,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I just wanted to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:42.94,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,If I became her pet, I could stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.11,0:29:53.25,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Although there was no sex involved, she needed me more than any other human.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.32,0:29:56.83,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Not human?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.79,0:30:00.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yup, I have no human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.96,0:30:06.13,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Isn't that kind of hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.61,0:30:12.04,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It may have been hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.17,0:30:17.78,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes it was super hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.95,0:30:23.02,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But sometimes I was super happy. So I needed her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.69,0:30:29.52,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,It sounds like a surreal story to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.19,0:30:31.33,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.96,0:30:35.66,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But it was a lot more pure than any real love relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.10,0:30:41.00,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You aren't such a bad person after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.44,0:30:44.74,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,You aren't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.67,0:30:51.75,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Please take care of Iwaya-san. She's actually a very fragile person.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.95,0:31:04.89,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,She never showed me her efforts nor her tears, but she was probably holding in a lot…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.79,0:31:09.90,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,At first, she didn't even know how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.30,0:31:14.64,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I don't know when she started practicing, but she soon became like a professional chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.54,0:31:17.64,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.34,0:31:21.78,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So the cooking was indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.24,0:31:23.11,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.48,0:31:26.48,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm getting a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.82,0:31:34.72,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.03,0:31:40.90,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Oh, really?! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.00,0:31:43.00,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.57,0:31:46.67,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,My wife is starting to have contractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.70,0:31:49.34,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I'm glad we got to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.58,0:31:56.44,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Congrats! Be a good papa to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.08,0:32:03.65,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Tell Iwaya-san "Congratulations", too!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.89,0:32:05.65,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.02,0:32:08.99,Petto_basic,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Because her birthday is tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.90,0:32:16.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.03,0:32:19.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.63,0:32:20.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.14,0:32:24.07,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be in a place like that, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.31,0:32:28.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I told you, you didn't have to come along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.91,0:32:31.25,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll help you when you're in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.25,0:32:35.55,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm the only girl friend you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.28,0:32:37.69,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.25,0:32:41.86,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Honestly, there are some things I envied about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.32,0:32:46.00,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, elite, and have everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.00,0:32:48.86,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,As for me, I'm always tied up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.17,0:32:55.57,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Personally, I'd like to see what happens between you and that pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.87,0:33:00.44,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yuri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.35,0:33:45.02,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm tired… I'm so exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.22,0:33:46.89,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,We can't find him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.26,0:33:49.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even though I mustered up the courage to come to places
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.76,0:33:52.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,like Ikebukuro and Shibuya, where all the young people seem to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.83,0:33:54.30,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Really…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.87,0:34:00.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yuri-chan. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.29,0:34:24.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.23,0:34:37.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What was I thinking, there's no way he'd fit into a small box like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.41,0:34:42.68,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.01,0:34:44.88,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.15,0:34:48.22,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Well I'll be darned, it's an abandoned kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.42,0:34:51.19,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,There, there…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.62,0:34:56.96,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what are you planning to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.96,0:34:59.59,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,I'm going to find the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.06,0:35:04.17,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,It's a shame that there are so many irresponsible owners out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.17,0:35:05.40,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,There, there…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.15,0:35:18.88,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.52,0:35:27.32,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.34,0:35:45.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.89,0:36:00.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.86,0:36:10.37,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let's go back home, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.18,0:36:23.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.22,0:36:35.56,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I take this hand now,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.13,0:36:40.53,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go back to being Momo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.76,0:36:45.27,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}That sweer, but bitter life as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.92,0:37:05.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.19,0:37:12.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's okay that I come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.41,0:37:24.41,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.71,0:37:29.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.62,0:37:37.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Do you have somewhere else to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.75,0:37:41.02,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't have anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.16,0:37:47.33,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Only your place, Sumire-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.03,0:37:58.21,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Yours is the only place… I can go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.42,0:38:43.69,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind if I don't get treated like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.25,0:38:48.36,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because in front of these tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:53.19,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can become a courageous hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.04,0:39:04.77,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,This feels great~
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.38,0:39:17.89,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wonder where he has been, getting so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.96,0:39:23.46,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, it's past 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.73,0:39:25.53,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.43,0:39:30.23,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Happy birthday! Here's your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.84,0:39:38.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,A shampoo certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.21,0:39:44.35,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Yup! I thought that once in a while, in return for your daily care, I could gently massage your scalp.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.35,0:39:45.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Like I need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.05,0:39:46.95,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,What?! Isn't that a little harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.52,0:39:49.38,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I took the time to write it with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.38,0:39:51.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not harsh. What is "bathing suit recommended" supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.56,0:39:56.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh! It's Destroyer King Hashimoto Shinya's autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.29,0:39:59.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I got punched a little, but he was a really good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.73,0:40:02.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wow, Momo! It's great that you got punched! You got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.60,0:40:04.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Where did you meet him?! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.87,0:40:08.54,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Where I met him is a secret…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.72,0:40:29.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.06,0:40:33.23,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Happy birthday! Sorry to call you all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.53,0:40:36.20,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I got out of work early, so is it all right if I go over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.93,0:40:40.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm… well…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.10,0:40:43.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Right now is a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.94,0:40:48.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,My younger sister is over right now and she wants to stay the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.38,0:40:51.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.08,0:40:55.42,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault for asking all of a sudden. I guess I'll see you in the day then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.42,0:40:56.42,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.89,0:41:06.86,Petto_basic_ending,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Shall we wait for twelve more hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.63,0:41:13.77,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay, right? We're going to see each other in twelve hours anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.44,0:41:17.97,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,I love you, Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.97,0:41:20.30,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait… don't jump on me like that! Your hair's wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.30,0:41:24.01,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Don't make such a fuss! Then dry my hair for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.01,0:41:25.05,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.48,0:41:27.72,Petto_basic_ending,Junpei,0,0,0,,So you went back to your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.72,0:41:30.52,Petto_basic_ending,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yup. Right now, she's on a date with her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.62,0:41:32.39,Petto_basic_ending,Junpei,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.62,0:41:36.52,Petto_basic_ending,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Takeshi~, one of your fans is here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.69,0:41:38.43,Petto_basic_ending,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, all right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.33,0:41:42.33,Petto_basic_ending,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.53,0:41:43.83,Petto_basic_ending,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.03,0:41:49.14,Petto_basic_ending,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,You're Goda Takeshi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.04,0:41:51.01,Petto_basic_ending,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.01,0:41:55.78,Petto_basic_ending,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This is a birthday present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.85,0:41:59.35,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.12,0:42:01.08,Petto_basic_ending,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.00,0:42:03.00,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.26,0:42:16.26,Petto_basic_ending,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.26,0:42:19.10,Petto_basic_ending,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Are you really that woman's pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.50,0:42:21.60,Petto_basic_ending,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yes, directly back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.54,0:42:24.97,Petto_basic_ending,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,You don't hesitate to answer immediately, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.97,0:42:26.37,Petto_basic_ending,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Nope, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.44,0:42:28.38,Petto_basic_ending,Takeshi,0,0,0,,By the way, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.38,0:42:32.85,Petto_basic_ending,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Then did you know that today, Hasumi-san is going to propose to that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.12,0:42:35.42,Petto_basic_ending,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I want you to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.15,0:42:40.99,Petto_basic_ending,Hasumi,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that I may return to Rio de Janeiro in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.79,0:42:46.26,Petto_basic_ending,Hasumi,0,0,0,,If that were to happen, I'd want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.00,0:42:50.83,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,It's accurate information.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.03,0:42:54.10,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I know that he bought her a ring from Bank Reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.74,0:42:58.04,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,If that were to happen, wouldn't you get thrown away?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.28,0:43:05.41,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I see. And just what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.91,0:43:09.68,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,You catch on fast. Then I'll be straight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.79,0:43:13.92,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I want Hasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.36,0:43:18.63,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,So I want you to steal that woman away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.90,0:43:27.84,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,If you don't know how to do it, I can teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:32.61,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.41,0:43:37.35,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,You can't win just by being on the offensive, so you're trying to break things from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.12,0:43:48.46,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Wow, you're really serious about Hasumi-kun. You're kinda cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.36,0:43:52.43,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I'm not serious about him. I just want him, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.63,0:43:58.97,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,So you seem to be pretty smooth with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.64,0:44:03.00,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,Then why don't you do something about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.00,0:44:05.81,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,If I could get her like that, I would have done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.64,0:44:10.98,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But she doesn't seem to want that, and maybe I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.62,0:44:17.62,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know what the kite's joy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.15,0:44:21.29,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,When I say kite, I mean the kind you fly for New Years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.23,0:44:30.57,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,The reason for the kite to fly happily in the sky is not because it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.50,0:44:35.67,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's because there's a string that will eventually tug it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.57,0:44:45.21,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Even if it could fly freely, no matter how high it flew… even if it could reach outer space, it wouldn't be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.65,0:44:48.28,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,I don't understand the point you're trying to make at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.12,0:44:51.85,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Beyond that string is a place to go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.69,0:44:58.73,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Even if it gets tattered and torn, or becomes useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.13,0:45:00.80,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,There is a gentle hand that will hold it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.60,0:45:05.30,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That's why I can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.00,0:45:13.04,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,For that, I would live the rest of my life as a useless creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.38,0:45:18.61,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thanks for the treat, even though I didn't drink anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.79,0:45:27.66,Petto_basic,Fukuhima,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I want you to steal that woman away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.82,0:45:30.96,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I don't have to be told by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.20,0:45:37.27,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I will never let go of that hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.94,0:45:51.85,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm not in a rush, but I just want an answer.